<p><strong>Bug A</strong> — Reaching the finish should load the next level. Right now the player just keeps playing the same level forever.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">if player.colliderect(finish):
    platforms, coins, enemies, finish = load_level(current_level)
</code></pre>
